What Makes an App Successful? A Google Play Store Analysis
----
Business Understanding
Problem Statement

The mobile application market is highly competitive, with millions of apps available on the Google Play Store. Developers face challenges in understanding what factors contribute to an app’s success, such as high ratings and large numbers of installs.

Without proper analysis, developers may fail to optimize their applications, resulting in low user engagement and poor performance in the market.

Goals
Identify key factors that influence app success
Help developers understand user preferences
Support better decision-making in app development
Objectives
Analyze relationships between app features (rating, size, price, category) and installs
